          "title": "Edward Scissorhands",
          "year": 1990,
          "note": "No. 2: her favorite; the fantastical version of his real life, so much of it in daylight."
        },
        {
          "title": "Batman Returns",
          "year": 1992,
          "note": "No. 3: ranked above Batman purely for Keaton and Michelle Pfeiffer."
        },
